Be a good husband:
Character: be a thoughtful husband, pursue your wife, be spontaneous, integrity, responsibility, passionate, dependable, disciplined, mature, strength, work hard, be astute, communicate, schedule, plan in advance, keep healthy habits, 
be a good provider, be smart where you put your resources.

