Integrity:
Marriage is no place for privacy.
White lies are full lies and the worst of humanity.
Withholding information is lying.
The shoe eventually drops on lies and bad patters/misdeeds.
A lie pulls someone high up by a flimsy string.
Act like everyone is watching --especially your wife.
